<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Fusilli carciofi e salmone – Ricette (e altro) di Pierre</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../style.css">
  <style id="recipe-layout-style">.recipe-page{
  max-width: 100%;
}
.recipe-page > h1{
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.recipe-page .recipe-content{
  width: 100%;
  max-width: min(100%, var(--reading));
}
.recipe-page .meta-grid,
.recipe-page .lead,
.recipe-page .block,
.recipe-page .notes,
.recipe-page .rp-license-wrap{
  max-width: min(100%, var(--reading));
}
.recipe-page .lead{
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.68);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
}
.recipe-page .lead h2:first-child,
.recipe-page .notes h2:first-child,
.recipe-page .block h2:first-child{
  margin-top: 0;
}
.recipe-page .rp-license-wrap{
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
}
.recipe-license{
  opacity: 0.9;
}
.recipe-license img{
  width: 100px;
  max-width: 100px;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}
@media (max-width: 760px){
  .recipe-page .lead{
    padding: 1rem 1rem;
  }
}</style>
  <style id="recipe-lightbox-style">.recipe-lightbox-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.88);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:2rem;z-index:9999;cursor:zoom-out;}
.recipe-lightbox-overlay.is-hidden{display:none !important;}
.recipe-lightbox-frame{max-width:96vw;max-height:96vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.75rem;align-items:center;}
.recipe-lightbox-frame img{display:block;max-width:96vw;max-height:88vh;width:auto;height:auto;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.45);background:#fff;}
.recipe-lightbox-caption{color:#fff;text-align:center;max-width:min(96vw,70rem);font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.35;}
main figure:not(.recipe-license) img{cursor:zoom-in;}</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
<header class="site-header">
  <a class="brand" href="../../index.html">Ricette (e altro) di Pierre</a>
  <nav>
    <a href="../../indici/ricette.html">Ricette</a>
    <a href="../../indici/ingredienti.html">Ingredienti</a>
    <a href="../../indici/fonti.html">Fonti</a>
    <a href="../../indici/geografia.html">Geografia</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<main class="recipe-page">
<main><h1>Fusilli carciofi e salmone</h1><div class="recipe-content"><section class="lead"><h2>Introduzione e contesto</h2><p></p></section><section class="meta-grid"><div class="meta-card"><strong>Autore</strong><span>Pierre Piccotti</span></div><div class="meta-card"><strong>Categoria</strong><span>Primi</span></div><div class="meta-card"><strong>Geografia</strong><span>Italia</span></div><div class="meta-card"><strong>Fonte</strong><span></span></div></section><section class="block"><h2>Ingredienti</h2><table class="recipe-table"><thead><tr><th>Ingrediente</th><th>Quantità</th><th>Unità</th><th>Note</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Salmone cotto a vapore</td><td>1</td><td>scatola</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Fusilli</td><td>1/2</td><td>Kg</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Carciofi "grassi"</td><td>3</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Aglio</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Sale</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Pepe</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Prezzemolo</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Olio</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></section><section class="block preparation-block"><h2>Preparazione</h2><ol class="steps"><li><p>Far rosolare leggermente i carciofi in un tegame con olio e aglio quindi stufare fino a che siano teneri; togliere dal fuoco.Aggiungere il salmone a pezzetti, una manciata di prezzemolo, sale e pepe.Scolare i fusilli al dente.Saltare il tutto nel tegame per qualche minuto, eventualmente aggiungendo un poco di olio.</p></li></ol></section><section class="notes"><h2>Note e osservazioni</h2><ul class="clean"><li>Per la cottura della pasta usare acqua ben salata e scolare con il condimento già pronto.</li><li>Indicazione di tempo presente nel testo: 5 minuti</li></ul></section><div class="rp-license-wrap"><div class="recipe-license"><img alt="Licenza Creative Commons BY-NC-SA" src="../../foto/licenze/Cc-by-nc-sa_icon.svg"/></div></div></div></main>
</main>
</div>
<script id="recipe-lightbox-script">(function(){
  function ensureLightbox(){
    let overlay = document.getElementById('recipeLightbox');
    if(overlay) return overlay;
    overlay = document.createElement('div');
    overlay.id = 'recipeLightbox';
    overlay.className = 'recipe-lightbox-overlay is-hidden';
    overlay.innerHTML = '<div class="recipe-lightbox-frame"><img alt=""><div class="recipe-lightbox-caption"></div></div>';
    document.body.appendChild(overlay);
    overlay.addEventListener('click', function(){ overlay.classList.add('is-hidden'); });
    document.addEventListener('keydown', function(ev){ if(ev.key === 'Escape') overlay.classList.add('is-hidden'); });
    return overlay;
  }
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(){
    const overlay = ensureLightbox();
    const outImg = overlay.querySelector('img');
    const caption = overlay.querySelector('.recipe-lightbox-caption');
    document.querySelectorAll('main img').forEach(function(img){
      if(img.closest('.recipe-license')) return;
      img.addEventListener('click', function(ev){
        ev.preventDefault();
        ev.stopPropagation();
        outImg.src = img.currentSrc || img.src;
        outImg.alt = img.alt || '';
        const fig = img.closest('figure');
        const cap = fig ? fig.querySelector('figcaption') : null;
        caption.textContent = (cap && cap.textContent.trim()) || img.alt || '';
        overlay.classList.remove('is-hidden');
      });
    });
  });
})();</script>
</body>
</html>
